data.description: This is a hidden gem with privacy, 3 Heavily treed acres, pipe fence with automatic gate, freshly painted exterior with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, large covered patio for entertaining, lots of windows cabinets and storage. Split bedrooms, well and septic.  No HOA, Large 40x60 shop with insulation, 2 Rooms each 20x20 one down stairs with bathroom and one upstairs.  Both the rooms have mini split AC units. Shop has sink and own Septic Tank, electricity, 2 14x14 insulated doors, big enough for a RV you can drive through.
